Package: pidgin-sipe
Section: net
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: gstreamer0.10-ffmpeg, gstreamer0.10-x
Description: Pidgin plugin for MS Office Communicator and MS Lync
 A third-party plugin for the Pidgin multi-protocol instant messenger.
 It implements the extended version of SIP/SIMPLE used by various products:
 .
     * Microsoft Lync Server 2010
     * Microsoft Office Communications Server (OCS 2007/2007 R2 and newer)
     * Microsoft Live Communications Server (LCS 2003/2005)
     * Reuters Messaging
 .
 With this plugin you should be able to replace your Microsoft Office
 Communicator client with Pidgin.

Package: pidgin-sipe-dbg
Section: debug
Priority: extra
Architecture: any
Depends: pidgin-sipe (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Pidgin plugin for MS Office Communicator and MS Lync (debug symbols)
 A third-party plugin for the Pidgin multi-protocol instant messenger.
 It implements the extended version of SIP/SIMPLE used by various products:
 .
     * Microsoft Lync Server 2010
     * Microsoft Office Communications Server (OCS 2007/2007 R2 and newer)
     * Microsoft Live Communications Server (LCS 2003/2005)
     * Reuters Messaging
 .
 This package contains debug symbols for pidgin-sipe that can help in
 tracing execution of the plugin and searching for bugs.
